twitch.tv/geor0se

Schedule

Geo is live on Twitch from 11:00 16:00 GMT Monday, Wednesday, Thursday and Friday.

Duties

Set a good example for the viewers in the community by being welcoming and friendly.

You are not required to take part in every stream, or chat excessively, but please only apply if you are available for the majority of Geo's stream schedule.

Some things you may have to help with during the streams:

  • Snoozing ads if Geo or another mod is unable to.
  • Welcoming in raiders, and giving the raid host a shout out.
  • Delete chat messages when required.
  • Time out users and even ban certain users who aren't being cooperative with Geo's stream rules.

Do not entertain any rudeness, this applies to chatters in the stream or players in Geo's lobbies during gameplay.
